---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="技术架构 — AEROS" description="AEROS 五层运行时架构：从硬件抽象到智能体治理执行，层层分明。" lang="zh">

  <!-- ═══ Header ═══ -->
  <section class="section" style="padding-bottom: var(--space-2xl);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">技术架构</div>
      <h1 class="page-title">一台机器人，一个 Agent</h1>
      <p class="page-desc">
        能力靠 ECM 加载，行为靠治理约束。
        不搞多智能体集群，不搞模型直连硬件。
        一个 Agent 管到底。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Architecture Philosophy ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="philosophy-grid">
        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <div class="philosophy-icon">&Delta;</div>
          <h3>一机一 Agent</h3>
          <p>每台机器人对应一个持久化 Agent。身份、状态、学习经验，贯穿整个运行周期不丢失。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <div class="philosophy-icon">&loz;</div>
          <h3>能力可插拔</h3>
          <p>Agent 本身不写死能力，而是按需加载。ECM 包独立安装、独立版本管理，随时升级和回滚。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="philosophy-card">
          <div class="philosophy-icon">&lambda;</div>
          <h3>治理不是可选项</h3>
          <p>每次能力调用都得过治理引擎。安全靠架构保证，不靠理想主义。审计链路完整记录，不做抽样。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Five-Layer Architecture (Interactive) ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">架构</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">五层运行时架构</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);">
        点击每一层，看看它负责什么。
      </p>

      <div class="arch-interactive">
        <div class="arch-layers">
          <button class="arch-btn active" data-layer="agent">
            <span class="arch-btn-num">5</span>
            <span class="arch-btn-name">Agent</span>
          </button>
          <button class="arch-btn" data-layer="governance">
            <span class="arch-btn-num">4</span>
            <span class="arch-btn-name">治理</span>
          </button>
          <button class="arch-btn" data-layer="ecm">
            <span class="arch-btn-num">3</span>
            <span class="arch-btn-name">ECM 包</span>
          </button>
          <button class="arch-btn" data-layer="runtime">
            <span class="arch-btn-num">2</span>
            <span class="arch-btn-name">运行时</span>
          </button>
          <button class="arch-btn" data-layer="embodiment">
            <span class="arch-btn-num">1</span>
            <span class="arch-btn-name">具身层</span>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="arch-details">
          <div class="arch-detail active" id="detail-agent">
            <h3>第 5 层：Agent</h3>
            <p class="arch-detail-desc">最上层，跑决策逻辑。每个 Agent 都有自己的身份、记忆和目标，是个持久化的实体。</p>
            <div class="arch-detail-grid">
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">决策引擎</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">对接大模型，负责规划和推理</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">状态管理器</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">Agent 状态跨会话、跨重启持久保存</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">目标追踪器</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">拆任务、盯进度、必要时重新规划</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">经验记忆</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">学到的行为、踩过的坑、适应性数据</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="arch-detail" id="detail-governance">
            <h3>第 4 层：治理</h3>
            <p class="arch-detail-desc">策略执行层。每次能力调用在真正执行前，都要过一遍当前生效的策略。</p>
            <div class="arch-detail-grid">
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">策略引擎</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">声明式语言，写清运行边界</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">监控器系统</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">实时盯住不变量，违规立刻触发</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">恢复编排器</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">记录 → 告警 → 干预 → 停机，逐级响应</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">审计记录器</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">每个决策和行动都有不可篡改的日志</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="arch-detail" id="detail-ecm">
            <h3>第 3 层：ECM 包</h3>
            <p class="arch-detail-desc">能力层。Agent 的能力以模块形式加载，每个模块都有版本号和契约绑定，随时可装可卸可回滚。</p>
            <div class="arch-detail-grid">
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">契约注册中心</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">六维类型化接口，连接 Agent 和硬件</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">包管理器</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">装、升、回滚，全部原子操作</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">兼容性校验器</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">装之前先看硬件和策略是否允许</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">影子执行器</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">新能力先在旁边跑，不碰生产环境</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="arch-detail" id="detail-runtime">
            <h3>第 2 层：运行时</h3>
            <p class="arch-detail-desc">执行层。管 Agent 的生老病死，调度任务，跑感知→决策→执行闭环，处理各种异常。</p>
            <div class="arch-detail-grid">
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">生命周期管理器</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">完整状态机：初始化、启动、暂停、恢复、停止、重启</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">任务调度器</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">按优先级调度，可抢占，保 deadline</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">执行闭环</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">感知→决策→执行，带超时兜底</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">故障处理器</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">重试 → 回退 → 降级 → 停机，分级应对</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="arch-detail" id="detail-embodiment">
            <h3>第 1 层：具身层</h3>
            <p class="arch-detail-desc">硬件抽象层。把五花八门的传感器、执行器和计算资源统一成标准接口。</p>
            <div class="arch-detail-grid">
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">传感器抽象</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">相机、LiDAR、IMU、力/扭矩——统一数据格式</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">执行器接口</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">臂、轮、爪、腿——统一控制 API</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">资源监控器</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">CPU、GPU、内存、电池——实时掌握资源状态</span>
              </div>
              <div class="arch-component">
                <span class="comp-name">硬件注册中心</span>
                <span class="comp-desc">自动发现设备，自动枚举能力</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ ROS 2 Relationship ═══ -->
  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">定位</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">AEROS 与 ROS 2</h2>

      <div class="ros-layout">
        <div class="ros-diagram">
          <img id="arch-svg" src="/images/arch-zh-dark.svg" alt="AEROS 架构 — AEROS 如何连接智能体与硬件" />
        </div>

        <div class="ros-text">
          <h3>不同层，不同问题</h3>
          <p>
            ROS 2 是通信中间件，管节点之间怎么传消息。
            AEROS 在 ROS 2 之上，管智能体怎么<em>跑</em>和怎么<em>治理</em>。
          </p>
          <p>
            打个比方：<strong>Linux 和 Kubernetes</strong> 的关系，就像 <strong>ROS 2 和 AEROS</strong>。
            Kubernetes 不是 Linux 的插件，而是在更高层解决不同的问题。
            AEROS 也一样。
          </p>
          <div class="ros-comparison">
            <div>
              <span class="ros-comp-label">ROS 2 管的</span>
              <span class="ros-comp-value">话题、服务、动作、节点、DDS 传输</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="ros-comp-label">AEROS 管的</span>
              <span class="ros-comp-value">Agent 生命周期、ECM 包、治理策略、审计链路</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ Open-Core Model ═══ -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">商业模式</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">开放核心，商业治理</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);">
        核心运行时完全开源，企业级治理能力商业化。
      </p>

      <div class="core-stack">
        <div class="core-layer core-commercial">
          <div class="core-left">
            <span class="core-name">治理控制台</span>
            <span class="core-desc">策略 DSL · 监控 · 审计 · 恢复编排</span>
          </div>
          <span class="core-license">企业许可</span>
        </div>
        <div class="core-layer core-open">
          <div class="core-left">
            <span class="core-name">ECM 包管理系统</span>
            <span class="core-desc">标准格式 · 契约 · 版本管理 · 兼容性校验</span>
          </div>
          <span class="core-license license-open">Apache 2.0</span>
        </div>
        <div class="core-layer core-open">
          <div class="core-left">
            <span class="core-name">运行时核心</span>
            <span class="core-desc">生命周期 · 调度 · 执行闭环 · 故障恢复</span>
          </div>
          <span class="core-license license-open">Apache 2.0</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="core-rationale">
        <p><strong>开源拉开发者，</strong>治理赚企业的钱。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══ CTA ═══ -->
  <section class="section" style="text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">看看背后的研究</h2>
      <p class="section-desc" style="margin: 0 auto var(--space-xl);">
        7 篇系统性论文，覆盖 AEROS 的架构、治理、进化、契约、联邦化和基准测试。
      </p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: var(--space-md); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="https://s20sc.github.io/aeros-project" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">查看研究计划</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/s20sc/aeros-runtime" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-secondary">查看源码 &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<script is:inline>
  document.querySelectorAll('.arch-btn').forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      document.querySelectorAll('.arch-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
      document.querySelectorAll('.arch-detail').forEach(d => d.classList.remove('active'));
      btn.classList.add('active');
      document.getElementById('detail-' + btn.dataset.layer).classList.add('active');
    });
  });
  function updateArchSvg() {
    const img = document.getElementById('arch-svg');
    if (!img) return;
    const theme = document.documentElement.getAttribute('data-theme') || 'dark';
    img.src = '/images/arch-zh-' + theme + '.svg';
  }
  updateArchSvg();
  const observer = new MutationObserver(updateArchSvg);
  observer.observe(document.documentElement, { attributes: true, attributeFilter: ['data-theme'] });
</script>

<style>
  .page-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .page-desc {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 600px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .section-alt {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  /* ═══ Philosophy ═══ */
  .philosophy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }
  .philosophy-card {
    background: var(--bg-base);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }
  .philosophy-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .philosophy-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .philosophy-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ═══ Interactive Arch ═══ */
  .arch-interactive {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    min-height: 400px;
  }
  .arch-layers {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .arch-btn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all var(--duration-short);
    text-align: left;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .arch-btn:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .arch-btn.active {
    border-color: var(--primary);
    background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.05);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .arch-btn-num {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .arch-btn.active .arch-btn-num {
    background: var(--primary);
    color: white;
  }
  .arch-btn-name {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .arch-detail {
    display: none;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: var(--space-xl);
  }
  .arch-detail.active { display: block; }
  .arch-detail h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .arch-detail-desc {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    max-width: 560px;
  }
  .arch-detail-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }
  .arch-component {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }
  .comp-name {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }
  .comp-desc {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  /* ═══ ROS Layout ═══ */
  .ros-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .ros-diagram {
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .ros-diagram img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }
  .ros-layer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }
  .ros-aeros { border-color: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.3); background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.05); }
  .ros-tag {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  .ros-arrow {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding: var(--space-sm) 0;
  }
  .ros-text h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
  .ros-text p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  .ros-text em { font-family: var(--font-display); font-style: normal; color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; }
  .ros-comparison {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }
  .ros-comparison > div {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .ros-comp-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  .ros-comp-value { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); }

  /* ═══ Open Core ═══ */
  .core-stack {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .core-layer {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--bg-surface);
  }
  .core-commercial { border-color: rgba(0, 194, 168, 0.3); }
  .core-left { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 2px; }
  .core-name { font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; color: var(--text-primary); }
  .core-desc { font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .core-license {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background: rgba(0, 194, 168, 0.1);
    color: var(--secondary);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .license-open {
    background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  .core-rationale {
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .core-rationale p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .core-rationale strong { color: var(--text-primary); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .philosophy-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .arch-interactive { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .arch-detail-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ros-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
